to take on the big stuff.

32:08.420 --> 32:10.420
But this is important.

32:10.420 --> 32:12.040
Low-income families are being
kicked out of their homes

32:12.040 --> 32:13.460
with nowhere else to go.

32:13.460 --> 32:14.920
