Teresa's approval?

32:20.290 --> 32:22.380
Not on a case like this.

32:22.380 --> 32:25.170
I just need to get our director
to sign off, and I will.

32:26.580 --> 32:28.790
But we need to keep
this between us until then.

32:32.580 --> 32:34.880
You said you wanted more to do.

32:34.880 --> 32:36.460
I'm gonna need
a right hand on this.

32:38.670 --> 32:39.790
Gael:
It went great.

32:39.790 --> 32:42.080
And you were right,
it was really good.

32:42.080 --> 32:43.710
I presented my work in person,

32:43.710 --> 32:45.540
