their questions.

32:45.540 --> 32:47.460
You think you got it?

32:47.460 --> 32:49.460
I think I'm in the running.

32:49.460 --> 32:51.960
Yeah, they said they're
gonna make a decision
in the next day or so.

32:52.790 --> 32:53.790
(phone beeps)

32:55.120 --> 32:56.920
Aah shit.
I gotta take this.
Let me call you back.

32:56.920 --> 32:58.580
(phone beeps)

