33:11.250 --> 33:13.210
I need the thumb drive
with the event archives on it.

33:16.830 --> 33:18.040
Gael, hold on a second.

33:18.040 --> 33:19.670
I need to find this thumb drive.

33:19.670 --> 33:20.710
I think I left it at Jamie's

33:20.710 --> 33:22.040
when I was there
the other night.

33:22.040 --> 33:23.710
Maybe I can get
Callie to let me in.

33:25.380 --> 33:27.170
Come on, come on, come on!

33:29.830 --> 33:31.420
Yes! Okay, Callie can let us in,

33:31.420 --> 33:32.830
but I don't have
time to go get it.

33:32.830 --> 33:33.960
I can get it.

33:35.000 --> 33:36.710
Okay, um, I will send
you the address.

33:36.710 --> 33:37.830
Blue thumb drive.

33:37.830 --> 33:39.330
I think it's
on the dining room table.

33:39.330 --> 33:40.120
Okay.

33:51.290 --> 33:53.250
I don't know how
to work for a company

33:53.250 --> 33:54.830
that sells itself
as being socially conscious,

33:54.830 --> 33:56.920
but doesn't want to be
too political or polarizing.

33:56.920 --> 33:58.830
Especially when it comes
to black liberation.

33:59.710 --> 34:00.830
I know.

34:00.830 --> 34:03.210
And pretty soon you'll be in
a place where you won't have to.

34:03.210 --> 34:05.710
But right now, you just have
to play the long game.

34:05.710 --> 34:08.000
You know how many
crappy companies I worked for
before I started my own?

34:08.000 --> 34:11.000
(scoffs)
I feel you.

34:11.000 --> 34:12.920
It sucks. Feels like
you're shrinking yourself

34:12.920 --> 34:14.380
to make them feel comfortable.

34:14.380 --> 34:15.420
I know.

34:16.710 --> 34:19.210
But, baby, you have a chance

34:19.210 --> 34:20.920
to make a real change
with this job.

34:20.920 --> 34:23.830
And to succeed after everything
you've been through?

34:23.830 --> 34:26.000
I mean, that's
an act of rebellion.

34:26.000 --> 34:27.750
That's protest, baby.

